<% layout('/layouts/boilerplate') %>

<section class="py-5">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-md-10">
        <div class="card p-4">
          <h3 class="mb-3">Help & Support — Website Help</h3>
          <p class="text-muted">Find answers to common user questions about using the website, uploading listings, bookings, payments, and account management. If your issue isn't listed, contact support at <strong>support@wanderstay.example</strong>.</p>

          <div class="accordion mt-4" id="helpAccordion">
            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                  1) How do I create a listing?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#helpAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  - Click <strong>Create Listing</strong> (top-right or via your profile). <br>
                  - Fill in the required fields: <em>title, description, price, location</em>. The more details and photos you add, the better your listing performs. <br>
                  - Upload clear photos and set a fair nightly price. Click <strong>Submit</strong> to publish.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                  2) How do I upload photos for my listing?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#helpAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  - Use the image uploader on the listing form. Choose clear, well-lit images (landscape orientation recommended). <br>
                  - After selecting files, wait for the upload indicator to finish before submitting. <br>
                  - If upload seems slow, try a smaller file size or a different browser. You can re-upload or replace images by editing the listing later.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="#collapseThree">
                  3) I don't see my listing after publishing — what now?
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#helpAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  - Refresh the page and check under <strong>My Listings</strong> in your profile. <br>
                  - Ensure you completed all required fields and clicked Submit. <br>
                  - If you still don't see it, please contact support with your account email and the listing title.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="#collapseFour">
                  4) Booking or payment related questions
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#helpAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  - To book a listing, select dates and follow the checkout flow. Payment confirmation appears on the bookings page and via email. <br>
                  - If payment fails, check your card details and bank. Try another payment method or contact your bank. <br>
                  - For refunds or cancellations, follow the cancellation policy shown on the listing or contact support with your booking ID.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="accordion-item">
              <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="#collapseFive">
                  5) Account & security — login, password, profile
                </button>
              </h2>
              <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#helpAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                  - To change your profile photo, go to <strong>Profile</strong> and upload an image. <br>
                  - If you forget your password, use the password reset option (if available) or contact support with your registered email. <br>
                  - Never share your password or verification codes with anyone.
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-4 text-muted small">
            Still need help? Email <strong>support@wanderstay.example</strong> with a brief description, your account email, and any listing or booking IDs.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
